      "Name": "Summary",
      "Value": "Microsoft will end OneDrive sync app updates on Windows 10 version 22H1 and earlier starting August 15, 2026. Devices on 22H2 or later will continue receiving updates until October 10, 2028. Users should upgrade to Windows 10 22H2 or Windows 11 to maintain full support and functionality."
